video.title: ONE PIECE
video.synopsis: Monkey D. Luffy sails with his crew of Straw Hat Pirates through the Grand Line to find the treasure One Piece and become the new king of the pirates.

episodes.synopsis: Young Monkey D. Luffy, a pirate himself, runs afoul of other pirates when they attack a cruise ship. Luckily for him, Luffy has the power of rubber.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Coby and Luffy arrive in a town to recruit Zoro. Peering over a wall, they see a young girl and a man approach the captured bounty hunter.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Zoro and Luffy work together to defeat Morgan as a team. Despite his relationship with Luffy and Zoro, Coby wishes to join the Marines.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: After seeing Shanks stand up against the bandit leader Higuma, a young Luffy declares that he will one day become the king of all pirates.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Luffy inadvertently saves Nami from her pursuers. Nami is told to blast Luffy with a Buggy Ball when she presents Luffy to Buggy.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: A dog swallows the key to the cage Luffy is inside. Mayor Boodle puts the wounded Zoro to sleep and shares the story of Chouchou the dog.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Boodle attempts to take on Buggy by himself, but Luffy stops the mayor from getting himself killed. Luffy inflates himself to deflect a Buggy Ball.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Luffy learns about Buggy's history with Shanks. Buggy hurls the upper half of his body toward Nami as she tries to get away with his treasure.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Captain Usopp takes aim at Luffy with his slingshot after leading his crew to confront a boat that bears Buggy's insignia.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Usopp is driven away from Kaya's mansion by her butler Klahadore. Luffy and Usopp witness two men discussing a nefarious plan.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: No one believes Usopp when he tries to warn the villagers that pirates are coming. Usopp lies about telling the truth and prepares to face the enemy.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Luffy and his crew decide to help Usopp. As they wait for the Black Cat Pirates on a hill, they realize that there is another way to come ashore.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Django accidentally affects Luffy when he hypnotizes his underlings to unleash their ferocity. Luffy's crew struggles against the Black Cat Pirates.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Kuro's strength shows no signs of deterioration. Zoro and the Meowban Brothers continue their fight. Luffy wakes up after being stepped on by Nami.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Luffy throws a punch toward Kuro. Usopp orders his young crew members to protect Kaya. Kuro reveals the plan he set in motion years ago.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Usopp's crew decides to stand their ground and fight in order to live. Kuro prepares to sacrifice his men in order to attack Luffy.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Usopp launches an explosive attack against Django as Luffy puts a dent in Kuro's plans. Kaya gives Luffy and his crew a ship to call their own.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hat Pirates paint their very own pirate insignia aboard the Going Merry. The crew meets a pirate named Gaimon on a legendary island.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Young Zoro meets Kuina, his dojo master's daughter. They both swear to strive to become the strongest sword-fighter in the world.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Zoro's old friend recovers from scurvy with lime. The Straw Hats head to the restaurant ship Baratie after realizing the importance of having a cook.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: After being beaten to a pulp by a chef named Sanji, Fullbody receives an urgent report: One of Krieg's men has escaped.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Gin brings a starving Krieg to Baratie. Sanji ignores the protestations of those around him and gives the infamous pirate some food.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Krieg demands the owner of the Baratie to hand over his old ship's log after learning that he is the legendary pirate Zeff.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Zoro spots the strongest swordsman in the world and challenges him to a duel. Mihawk, however, decides to accept his challenge with only a dagger.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Luffy launches himself toward Krieg's crew. When Sanji and the crew of the Baratie prepare for battle, Pearl emerges from the sea.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Gin points a gun at Zeff and asks Sanji to disembark. Sanji remembers his past as he starts to lose consciousness from Pearl's punches.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Luffy tries to sink the Baratie in order to take the objective away from Krieg. Gin steps in as Pearl charges toward Sanji and Luffy.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Krieg has launched his deadly MH5 poison gas bomb. Luffy fearlessly dashes toward Krieg through a barrage of projectiles.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: The battle between Luffy and Krieg rages on. Luffy lands punch after punch on Krieg's armor to get through his defenses.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Luffy recruits Sanji to join his crew, but Sanji is reluctant to leave the restaurant. The other cooks put on an act to help Sanji make up his mind.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: During their pursuit of Nami, Yosaku explains to Luffy and Sanji that Arlong is a powerful fishman. Nami, Zoro and the others arrive in Arlong Park.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Luffy and Sanji beat up Momoo the giant sea cow. Nami's adoptive older sister Nojiko helps Usopp. A tied-up Zoro throws himself into the water.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Zoro heads to rescue Usopp from Choo. Nami confirms her intention to buy her home village after stabbing Usopp to avoid suspicion.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Luffy refuses to believe that Nami would kill Usopp. Nami's arrival triggers a tense situation between Zoro and Sanji. Luffy suddenly goes to sleep.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Zoro and the others listen as Nojiko talks about the past. While growing up under Belle-Mre's care, Nami dreamt of drawing a map of the world.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Belle-Mre has enough money to pay for her own survival, but she confesses to Arlong that she has two daughters who she can't provide for.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Captain Nezumi comes to confiscate Nami's stolen possessions. Nojiko tries to stop her furious sister from approaching Nezumi.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Luffy punches Arlong and sends him flying shortly after entering Arlong Park. Arlong picks Luffy up and throws him into the sea.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Zoro struggles to remain standing as the wound he sustained earlier from Mihawk holds him back. Genzo tries to free Luffy's legs from the rock.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Sanji dives into the water to find that Luffy is already receiving help. Kuroobi takes the opportunity to strike as Sanji lets his guard down.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Arlong forces Nami to choose between rejoining his crew or fighting to the last alongside her fellow villagers. Luffy regains consciousness.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Luffy puts a set of Arlong's regenerating teeth into his own mouth and bites back. Arlong goes into the sea to perform a special attack.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: Furious that Nami was used as a map-making tool, Luffy destroys the room she used to work in. Nezumi calls for a bounty to be put on Luffy's head.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: The islanders celebrate. Luffy gobbles up a storm. Nami pays her respects to Belle-Mre. Dr. Nako stitches Zoro up and removes Nami's tattoo.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: The bounty on Luffy is worth a whopping 30 million berries. Kaya is delighted to spot Usopp's head in Luffy's wanted ad. Shanks receives news.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Buggy seethes with vengeance after his fight with Luffy. He gets into a scuffle with Gaimon on his island when he is mistaken for a poacher.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Buggy's crew gets captured by cannibals after holding a funeral for their fallen leader. Buggy wreaks havoc after becoming whole again.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: Nami, Usopp, Sanji and Zoro head into Logue Town to shop for various things. Luffy goes straight to the scaffold where Gold Roger was executed.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Captain Smoker comes to arrest Luffy as he tries to climb the execution scaffold. Zoro obtains two swords from a weapon seller.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: Usopp faces bounty hunter Daddy Masterson in a duel after losing out on buying a pair of sniper goggles because of his daughter.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Sanji enters a cooking contest against Carmen, a woman who strives to become the best chef in all of East Blue.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Luffy climbs the scaffold and takes in the very last view the pirate king would have seen. Buggy appears and tries to execute Luffy on the scaffold.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: A thunderstorm illuminates Logue Town. Smoker turns his attention to Luffy after capturing the Buggy Pirates and Alvida.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: A little girl named Apis meets the Straw Hats after escaping from a Marine ship. Luffy and his crew decide to go on a detour to take her home.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: The Going Merry escapes a Calm Belt on a Sea King's sneeze and arrives at Warship Island, where the descendants of Lost Island live.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats help Apis escort an old dragon down a mountain in order to take him back home to Lost Island.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: Eric comes after the Going Merry. The dragon remembers the location of Lost Island. The Staw Hats arrive on an island that doesn't appear on any map.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: The crew only finds ruins on the island. The dragon remembers the real location of its home. Zoro deals with Eric while the others escort the dragon.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Marine vessels surround the Going Merry. Eric earns the ire of Nelson when he betrays him by taking off with Apis and the dragon.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Luffy throws back the harpoon Nelson shot at the dragon. The sky fills with other dragons as their nest emerges for the first time in a millennium.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Luffy fights Eric to protect Apis and her determination to save the dragons' nest. The Straw Hats head to a waterway that leads to the Grand Line.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats meet a lighthouse keeper named Crocus after the Going Merry is swallowed whole by a giant island whale called Laboon.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Fifty years have passed since Laboon was left in Crocus's care. Laboon rams his head against the Red Line as he waits for his friends to return.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: The Going Merry heads to an island with Mr. 9 and Ms. Wednesday. To their surprise, the Straw Hats receive a grand welcome from the islanders.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Zoro takes his new swords out on a test run against a mob of bounty hunters. After facing Ms. Monday, Zoro deals with Mr. 8.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Mr. 9 fights to protect Vivi from Mr. 5 and Ms. Valentine. Igaram begs Zoro to escort Vivi safely back to her kingdom.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: Nami stops the fight between fists and swords. Luffy agrees to help Vivi after learning about the Baroque Works' plan to take over her kingdom.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: Coby continues to work toward his dream as he works at a Marine base with Morgan's son Helmeppo. While being handed over, Morgan runs away from Garp.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Luffy learns from a newspaper that Coby is in the Grand Line. Garp makes a discovery about Coby as he oversees his training with Helmeppo.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats arrive at Little Garden, their second stop in the Grand Line. Luffy and Vivi go exploring and encounter a dinosaur on the island.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: Broggy the giant asks for a drink from Nami and Usopp, while Luffy is saved by another giant named Dorry. The two giants clash in a century-old feud.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: Usopp stares in awe as the two giants fight over their honor. Dorry blames the Straw Hats when the drink he received from them explodes.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Zoro and Nami disappear in the jungle while the giants continue their fight. Broggy moves in to strike when Dorry loses his footing on Mr. 3's wax.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Broggy finds out who placed the bomb in Dorry's drink. Mr. 3 captures Broggy and sets Vivi, Zoro and Nami on a giant candle display.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: Zoro and the others get covered in wax faster after Luffy takes action. Luffy gets hypnotized and rejects the idea of helping his friends.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: Mr. 3 goes on the offensive after Usopp snaps Luffy back to his senses. Usopp and Karoo prepare a rope as a wick to light the giant candle display.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Tears stream out of Broggy's eyes like waterfalls as he mourns his fallen rival. Sanji speaks to Mr. 0 at Mr. 3's hideout.
episodes.title: Episode 77

seasons.title: Enter Chopper at the Winter Island

episodes.synopsis: The Going Merry and the Straw Hats blast out of a giant goldfish with help from their friends. Bon Clay receives an order. Nami falls gravely ill.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: Wapol and his crew attack the Going Merry as snow falls all around them. Smoker intercepts the conversation between Sanji and Mr. 0.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Vivi continues to ask for a doctor after the villagers turn their guns toward the crew. A man named Dalton leads Luffy and the others into town.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Kureha treats a boy in the next town over as Luffy and the others encounter giant rabbits. Dalton reveals Wapol's past misdeeds.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: The herd of giant rabbits starts an avalanche. Dalton is injured when he stands up against Wapol. Luffy helps a young giant rabbit.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: Chess and Kuromarimo are intercepted by giant rabbits. Luffy climbs the Drum Rockies with Nami and Sanji. Vivi and the others arrive back in Bighorn.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: Nami meets Chopper after receiving treatment. Luffy and Sanji try to eat Chopper. Villagers find Dalton buried in the snow.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: Luffy asks Chopper to join the crew. Kureha talks to Nami and Sanji about Hiriluk, a doctor who continued to treat patients during the doctor hunt.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Chopper finds mushrooms to treat the ailing Hiriluk. Having completed his many years of research, Hiriluk asks Kureha to teach Chopper medicine.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: Kureha tells Wapol that she turned the castle into a memorial for Hiriluk. Wapol finds an opportunity to start chomping down on Chopper.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: Chopper gains a deeper understanding of what it means to be a pirate as he watches Luffy defend Hiriluk's flag. Doctors volunteer to save Dalton.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: After getting kicked by Luffy, Wapol declares that he will transform himself into a human weapon. Dalton and the others head to the castle.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: Nami is allowed to leave the castle after making a deal with Kureha. Chopper decides to join the Straw Hats, but Kureha refuses to let him go.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: Chopper realizes how much Kureha loves him as the Straw Hats celebrate their newest member aboard the Going Merry. Dalton hears about a man named Ace.
episodes.title: Episode 91

episodes.synopsis: Crocodile starts a sandstorm and instantly mummifies the pirates that were looting a harbor town. The Straw Hats fish Bon Clay out of the sea.
episodes.title: Episode 92

episodes.synopsis: Luffy runs off to find an eatery in Nanohana. Sanji volunteers to go shopping for Vivi. Chopper accidentally gets taken away in a supply wagon.
episodes.title: Episode 93

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats spot Tashigi and Smoker while looking for Luffy. Smoker chases Luffy after being blasted out of a restaurant with Ace.
episodes.title: Episode 94

episodes.synopsis: Ace fights Smoker. Luffy declines Aces offer to join the Whitebeard Pirates and says he will fight their captain to become the king of all pirates.
episodes.title: Episode 95

episodes.synopsis: Vivi sends Karoo on a mission to deliver a letter to Alubarna. Ace suspects there must be more to Crocodile's plan than to just take over the kingdom.
episodes.title: Episode 96

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats travel through the desert with Vivi and Ace. Luffy rescues a camel from a carnivorous plant after getting tricked by a flock of birds.
episodes.title: Episode 97

episodes.synopsis: Nami and Vivi ride ahead as Luffy and the others follow them on foot. Ace gets separated from the group while Luffy goes wild after eating cactuses.
episodes.title: Episode 98

episodes.synopsis: Ace helps himself to food and water from Camu and his band of fake rebels. Vivi decides to test if the fake rebels' hearts are in the right place.
episodes.title: Episode 99

episodes.synopsis: Young Vivi and her friend Koza lead a group of kids called the Sand-Sand Clan. Koza gets injured while trying to protect Vivi from kidnappers.
episodes.title: Episode 100

episodes.synopsis: A bounty hunter known as Scorpion finds Ace. When the two enter a fight, it soon becomes clear that Scorpion lied about defeating Blackbeard.
episodes.title: Episode 101

episodes.synopsis: Luffy goes on another hallucinatory rampage and gets lost in the desert with Zoro and Chopper away from the rest of the crew.
episodes.title: Episode 102

episodes.synopsis: The enemy leaders assemble and head out to see Crocodile in Rainbase. The Straw Hats and Vivi arrive in Yuba and find it deserted.
episodes.title: Episode 103

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats and Vivi spend the night in Yuba at an inn. At a casino in Rainbase, Crocodile unveils Operation Utopia.
episodes.title: Episode 104

episodes.synopsis: Vivi decides to head straight to Rainbase. Upon their arrival, the Straw Hats immediately have an encounter with Smoker.
episodes.title: Episode 105

episodes.synopsis: Luffy and the others run from Smoker inside Raindinners and go straight into a cage. The time has come for Operation Utopia to begin.
episodes.title: Episode 106

episodes.synopsis: Bon Clay masquerades as King Cobra and confesses to the people of Nanohana that he had been taking their rain. A guard aims his gun at Koza.
episodes.title: Episode 107

episodes.synopsis: The rebel army makes their way toward Alubarna. As Crocodile prepares to head to the capital himself, he receives a call from a Mr. Prince.
episodes.title: Episode 108

episodes.synopsis: Chopper draws Crocodile's attention by calling himself Mr. Prince. Sanji kicks a banana gator to get the key out of its stomach.
episodes.title: Episode 109

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats and Vivi start to take off toward Alubarna atop a giant crab, but Luffy decides to stay behind to deal with Crocodile.
episodes.title: Episode 110

episodes.synopsis: Crocodile throws Luffy into a pit of quicksand. Vivi and the others cross the river and meet up with Karoo and the Supersonic Duck Squadron.
episodes.title: Episode 111

episodes.synopsis: The rebel army is on their way to Alubarna to confront the royal army. The Baroque Works agents see six cloaked figures heading their way.
episodes.title: Episode 112

episodes.synopsis: Sanji tells Usopp to help Chopper and runs to be at Vivi's side. Two members of the Supersonic Duck Squad save Vivi and Karoo from Bon Clay.
episodes.title: Episode 113

episodes.synopsis: Usopp and Chopper are in trouble; Mr. 4 hurls exploding baseballs at them as Ms. Merry Christmas maneuvers through tunnels in the sand.
episodes.title: Episode 114

episodes.synopsis: Despite receiving serious injuries, Usopp continues to stand up against Ms. Merry Christmas and Mr. 4 with Chopper. Sanji fights Bon Clay.
episodes.title: Episode 115

episodes.synopsis: Mr. 1 and Ms. Doublefinger zero in on Zoro and Nami. Sanji spots a flaw in Bon Clay's fighting technique.
episodes.title: Episode 116

episodes.synopsis: Nami goes up against Ms. Doublefinger with the new weapon that Usopp made for her. Crocodile asks King Cobra a question.
episodes.title: Episode 117

episodes.synopsis: Crocodile reveals a sinister plan after hearing that Cobra does not know the location of Pluton. Nami starts to get the hang of Clima Tact.
episodes.title: Episode 118

episodes.synopsis: Zoro realizes that trying to defeat Mr. 1 would be like trying to cut through steel. As their battle continues, Zoro remembers his teacher's story.
episodes.title: Episode 119

episodes.synopsis: There is less than half an hour left until detonation. Koza realizes Crocodile's role in everything. Vivi and Koza order their armies to stand down.
episodes.title: Episode 120

episodes.synopsis: Baroque Works infiltrators start up a fight between the two sides. When Vivi refuses to give up, Crocodile holds her over the edge of the palace.
episodes.title: Episode 121

episodes.synopsis: Vivi warns Zoro and the others about the threat in the plaza. Luffy faces Crocodile. Ms. All Sunday forces Cobra to guide her to a certain location.
episodes.title: Episode 122

episodes.synopsis: Luffy gets rehydrated. Crocodile's partnership with Ms. All Sunday comes to an end. Vivi realizes where the cannon could be hidden.
episodes.title: Episode 123

episodes.synopsis: Luffy challenges Crocodile to another battle. Everyone aside from Pell assembles at the clocktower with help from Tashigi and the Marines.
episodes.title: Episode 124

episodes.synopsis: Luffy continues to fight Crocodile. Nami comes up with an idea to get Vivi up to the top of the clocktower to stop the cannon.
episodes.title: Episode 125

episodes.synopsis: In spite of everything, the fighting still continues. Luffy hits Crocodile with a powerful storm of punches. Vivi's voice rings out for all to hear.
episodes.title: Episode 126

episodes.synopsis: Chaka orders his men to throw down their weapons. Igaram has a young witness from Nanohana explain that an imposter was pretending to be Cobra.
episodes.title: Episode 127

episodes.synopsis: The Straw Hats bring the palace to life. Hina secures the harbor to catch the pirates. The fugitives take off on the Supersonic Duck Squadron.
episodes.title: Episode 128

episodes.synopsis: Hina attacks the Going Merry and Bon Clay's ship. Bon Clay comes up with a diversion. The Straw Hats and Vivi display their sign of their friendship.
episodes.title: Episode 129

episodes.synopsis: Hina demonstrates a special skill. The citizens of Alabasta start to rebuild their country. A stowaway appears on the Going Merry.
episodes.title: Episode 130
